{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <p>許多人都有設定健身目標卻難以持之以恆的經驗，每次都信誓旦旦，卻在「Just one day」後功虧一簣，讓健身房會籍蒙塵，只能期待新的一年重新開始，而OnTrack這款健身夥伴App，今天限時免費，它能有效打破這個惡性循環，幫助你真正達成健身目標，非常適合所有渴望提升運動習慣但容易鬆懈的使用者。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/460x460bb-75-75.webp\" alt=\"限時免費\">\n    <h2>真實夥伴零藉口打卡</h2>\n    <p>OnTrack的核心機制在於與你真實認識的夥伴互相督促，透過GPS驗證的打卡機制，確保你確實出現在健身房，每一次的打卡與缺席，夥伴都能即時得知，這種真實人際關係的壓力，遠比冰冷的提醒更具效力，它能幫助你建立起驚人的運動連勝紀錄，並在困難時互相鼓勵，讓運動習慣不再是孤軍奮戰，而是充滿支持的共同旅程。</p>\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-64-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-65-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-66-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-67-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-68-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/1320x2868bb-69-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"App Screenshot\">\n    <ul>\n      <li>應用名稱：OnTrack – Gym Accountability</li>\n      <li>應用類別：Health &amp; Fitness</li>\n      <li>下載位置：App Store</li>\n    </ul>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-20T20:35:25.386279+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":379,"images":7,"source":"New MobileLife","fallback":"none"}}